OL,3,CFoden and Palmer left out: Who is in
OL,4,CEngland's World Cup squad?
OL,6,FEngland have named their 26-man World
OL,7,FCup squad, but big-name players like
OL,8,FCole Palmer and Phil Foden have been
OL,9,Fleft out.
OL,11,FManager Thomas Tuchel is hoping to end
OL,12,Fthe country's 60-year wait to hold a
OL,13,Fmajor trophy in June.
OL,15,FHarry Maguire, Adam Wharton, Morgan
OL,16,FGibbs-White and Luke Shaw are others
OL,17,Fwho have been overlooked.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
