OL,3,CFoden and Palmer left out: Who is in
OL,4,CEngland's World Cup squad?
OL,6,FMeanwhile, Aston Villa striker Ollie
OL,7,FWatkins has picked up a place after
OL,8,Fhelping his side win the Europa League
OL,9,Fon Wednesday, alongside Al-Ahli's Ivan
OL,10,FToney, who has scored 32 goals in 32
OL,11,Fgames in the Saudi league this season.
OL,13,FSo who is in England's squad and who
OL,14,Fhas been left out?
OL,16,FWhose made it?
OL,18,FGoalkeepers: Jordan Pickford
OL,19,F(Everton), Dean Henderson (Crystal
OL,20,FPalace), James Trafford (Manchester
OL,21,FCity)
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
