OL,3,CFoden and Palmer left out: Who is in
OL,4,CEngland's World Cup squad?
OL,6,FForwards: Harry Kane (Bayern Munich),
OL,7,FIvan Toney (Al-Ahli), Ollie Watkins
OL,8,F(Aston Villa), Bukayo Saka (Arsenal),
OL,9,FNoni Madueke (Arsenal), Marcus
OL,10,FRashford (Barcelona), Anthony Gordon
OL,11,F(Newcastle)
OL,13,FWho has been left out?
OL,15,FCole Palmer
OL,17,FPalmer burst onto the international
OL,18,Fscene at Euro 2024 under Gareth
OL,19,FSouthgate.
