OL,3,CFoden and Palmer left out: Who is in
OL,4,CEngland's World Cup squad?
OL,6,FComing off the bench against Spain in
OL,7,Fthe final, he equalised within three
OL,8,Fminutes, buying some time for a Three
OL,9,FLions comeback - but England went on
OL,10,Fto lose the game.
OL,12,FHe was just 22 at the time and went on
OL,13,Fto win both England's men's player of
OL,14,Fthe year and the PFA young player of
OL,15,Fthe year award.
OL,17,FBut this season has been a difficult
OL,18,Fone.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
