OL,3,CFoden and Palmer left out: Who is in
OL,4,CEngland's World Cup squad?
OL,6,FPalmer has scored nine goals in 25
OL,7,Fgames during an injury-hit campaign
OL,8,Ffor Chelsea, who finished eighth in
OL,9,Fthe Premier League.
OL,11,FFoden's form has not been great either.
OL,13,FHe scored six goals in five games just
OL,14,Fbefore Christmas, which looked like a
OL,15,Freturn to form, but he hasn't scored
OL,16,Fsince
OL,18,FIt is a big drop from 2023-24, when he
OL,19,Fscored 19 Premier League goals and 27
OL,20,Fin all competitions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
