OL,3,CFoden and Palmer left out: Who is in
OL,4,CEngland's World Cup squad?
OL,6,FHarry Maguire
OL,8,FMaguire said he was "shocked and
OL,9,Fgutted" to have been left out.
OL,11,FHe had been part of the England squad
OL,12,Fin March, his first call-up under
OL,13,FTuchel.
OL,15,FHe posted on Instagram on Thursday: "I
OL,16,Fwas confident I could of (sic) played
OL,17,Fa major part this summer for my
OL,18,Fcountry after the season I've had.
OL,19,FI've been left shocked and gutted by
OL,20,Fthe decision."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
