OL,3,CFoden and Palmer left out: Who is in
OL,4,CEngland's World Cup squad?
OL,6,FMaguire played at the 2018 and 2022
OL,7,FWorld Cups and was a key figure in
OL,8,FEngland's run to the Euro 2020 final.
OL,10,FHe missed Euro 2024 due to an injury
OL,11,Fand, after 18 months out of the
OL,12,Finternational picture, returned to
OL,13,Fplay in both of England's March
OL,14,Ffriendlies under Tuchel.
